title: Craft Pizza Dinner Cheese & Pepperoni | 4 Servings
description: When it comes to pizza, we would call ourselves aficiona-doughs! Crust us when we say that these classic pies made with light and fluffy focaccia are just as tasty as they are easy. Both pies are made with premium mozzarella and tomato sauce; one is plain cheese and the other is topped with pepperoni. The best part? They’re ready in less than 20 minutes. So, let Dad take a load off for pizza night—it’s the yeast you can do!

